00:07:53.272 --> 00:07:55.272
Kailangan muna nating kumuha ng tagapamahala ng site.

00:07:56.942 --> 00:07:58.342
Kailan mo gustong makipagkita?

00:08:03.542 --> 00:08:05.882
(Ji Eun Oh)

