00:08:52.262 --> 00:08:53.492
Tapos sasamahan na lang kita.

00:09:02.072 --> 00:09:04.002
Cheol Min, gusto mong sumabay sa amin ng tanghalian?

00:09:05.972 --> 00:09:08.682
