00:09:17.522 --> 00:09:21.192
I have that lunch meeting with the newly signed coordinators.

00:09:21.192 --> 00:09:22.362
Sabi ko sayo, remember?

00:09:26.192 --> 00:09:28.662
- Ngayon ba iyon? - Oo.

00:09:29.702 --> 00:09:32.602
